'''马克·加蒂斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Mark Gatiss'''}}，{{IPAc-en|icon|ˈ|g|eɪ|.|t|ɪ|s|}} {{respell|GAY|tis}};<ref>{{Cite episode | title = Science of Christmas | url = http://downloads.bbc.co.uk/podcasts/radio4/timc/timc_20111226-1700a.mp3 | accessdate = 2011-12-28 | series = The Infinite Monkey Cage | serieslink = The Infinite Monkey Cage | credits = Presented by [[:en:Brian_Cox_(physicist)|Brian Cox]] and [[:en:Robin_Ince|Robin Ince]] | network = [[:en:BBC|BBC]] | station = [[:en:BBC_Radio_4|BBC Radio 4]] | airdate = 26 December 2011 | seriesno = 5 | number = 6 | time = 2:28 | quote = There is still a 49% chance that his name will be mispronounced. So please welcome Mark Gatiss not Gatiss. | archive-date = 2011-12-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111230034431/http://downloads.bbc.co.uk/podcasts/radio4/timc/timc_20111226-1700a.mp3 | dead-url = no }}</ref>{{bd|1966年|10月17日}}）是一位英格兰[[演員|演员]]、[[編劇|编剧]]和小说作家。他知名于是[[喜剧|喜剧]]《[[绅士联盟|绅士联盟]]》的一员，同时写和演了电视剧《[[神秘博士|神秘博士]]》和《[[神探夏洛克|神探夏洛克]]》，参与2020年电影《[[困在时间里的父亲|困在时间里的父亲]]》。

==个人生活==

加蒂斯出生于英格兰[[:en:Sedgefield|塞奇菲尔德]]<ref name=guardian2010-10-11>{{cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/2010/oct/11/mark-gatiss-first-men-moon |title=Mark Gatiss: Rocket man |date=2010-10-11 |newspaper=[[:en:The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |last=Jeffries |first=Stuart |location=London |accessdate=2012-02-08 |archive-date=2012-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120520181013/http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/2010/oct/11/mark-gatiss-first-men-moon |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在[[:en:Edwardian_era|爱德华]]的精神病医院对面长大，他的父母在这家医院里工作。他小时候酷爱在电视上观看《[[神秘博士|神秘博士]]》和[[:en:Hammer_Horror|Hammer恐怖电影]]，阅读[[夏洛克·福尔摩斯|夏洛克·福尔摩斯]]和[[赫伯特·乔治·威尔斯|赫伯特·乔治·威尔斯]]和收集化石。这些爱好刺激了他成年后的创造性工作。<ref name=telegraphgeek /><ref name=sundayherald>{{cite news |title=Renaissance gentleman |author=Stephen Phelan |newspaper=[[:en:The_Sunday_Herald|The Sunday Herald]] |date=2004-11-07 |accessdate=2010-11-23 |url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_qn4156/is_20041107/ai_n12591433 |archive-date=2009-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090913005720/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_qn4156/is_20041107/ai_n12591433/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=guardian2004>{{cite news |title=A league of his own |author=Angelique Chrisafis |newspaper=[[:en:The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=2004-11-03 |accessdate=2010-11-24 |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/books/2004/nov/03/fiction.angeliquechrisafis |location=London |archive-date=2012-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120331133030/http://www.guardian.co.uk/books/2004/nov/03/fiction.angeliquechrisafis |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=leagueofgentlemen>{{cite web |title=Film Info. Interview with Steve Pemberton and Mark Gatiss |publisher=[[绅士联盟|The League of Gentlemen]].co.uk |date=2004-11-07 |accessdate=2010-11-24 |url=http://www.leagueofgentlemen.co.uk/newopen.shtml |archive-date=2011-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716061106/http://www.leagueofgentlemen.co.uk/newopen.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

他在[[:en:Newton_Aycliffe|纽顿·艾克利夫]]上了[[:en:Heighington_CE_Primary_School|Heighington CE小学]]和[[:en:Woodham_Community_Technology_College|Woodham综合学校]]；比加蒂斯小两年的[[:en:Paul_Magrs|保罗·马规茨]]也在后者上学，也写了《神秘博士》。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-30117544_ITM|title=Remembering Heighington's past with pride; The headteacher|newspaper=The Northern Echo|date=2007-03-26|quote=One Heighington alumnus is actor Mark Gattis, the star of hit comedies The League of Gentlemen and Little Britain.|accessdate=2012-02-08|archive-date=2012-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018080807/http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-30117544_ITM|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Golly goth |first=Steve |last=Pratt |newspaper=[[:en:The_Northern_Echo|The Northern Echo]] |date=2007-05-08 |url=http://www.thenorthernecho.co.uk/leisure/1383869.Golly_goth/ |accessdate=2010-06-25 |quote=Coincidentally, another Doctor Who fan and novel writer, The League of Gentlemen's Mark Gatiss also went to Woodhall, where he was two years above Magrs and in the same drama group. |archive-date=2012-09-12 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120912035351/http://www.thenorthernecho.co.uk/leisure/1383869.Golly_goth/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

他是一名公开的同性恋者，当选《[[獨立報|獨立報周日]]》评选的英国2010年和2011年<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/news/the-iiosi-pink-list-2011-2374595.html | title=The IoS Pink List 2011 | location=London | work=The Independent | first=Ian | last=Herbert | date=2011-10-23 | accessdate=2012-02-08 | archive-date=2011-10-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111025211852/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/news/the-iiosi-pink-list-2011-2374595.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>最有影响力的同性恋者的粉红色名单<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/news/the-iiosi-pink-list-2010-2040472.html|title=The IoS Pink List 2010|publisher=[[獨立報|獨立報周日]]|date=2010-08-01|accessdate=2010-08-01|quote=The League of Gentlemen star is set for a bonanza 2010. As well as co-creating the BBC's acclaimed Sherlock Holmes reboot, he'll soon be seen in his adaptation of HG Wells's First Men in the Moon. An appearance in an Alan Ackybourn revival at the National Theatre is also mooted.|location=London|archive-date=2010-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100802052109/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/news/the-iiosi-pink-list-2010-2040472.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他与演员Ian Hallard有[[英國民事伴侶關係|英國民事伴侶關係]]，兩人均在BBC電視劇《[[新世紀福爾摩斯|新世紀福爾摩斯]]》第二季中有演出（Ian Hallard在劇中第二季第三集飾演[[莫里亞蒂教授|莫里亞蒂教授]]的辯護律師），拥有一只[[拉布拉多尋回犬|拉布拉多尋回犬]]「Bunsen」。<ref name="Scot interview">{{cite web |last=Randall |first=Lee |url=http://thescotsman.scotsman.com/features/The-Monday-Interview-Mark-Gatiss.4699282.jp |title=The Monday Interview: Mark Gatiss - Top of the League - The Scotsman |publisher=Thescotsman.scotsman.com |date=2008-11-17 |accessdate=2010-10-28 |quote=Amid all this activity, Gatiss found time, last spring, to get married. He and Ian have been together for nearly a decade... He and Ian are the devoted 'parents' of Bunsen, a Labrador retriever. |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101126135101/http://thescotsman.scotsman.com/features/The-Monday-Interview-Mark-Gatiss.4699282.jp |archive-date=2010-11-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>为实现他的另一个童年梦想，他曾在伦敦的家修建一个[[维多利亚时代|维多利亚时代]]实验室。<ref name=telegraphgeek>{{cite news |title=Mark Gatiss: the journey of a geek made good |author=Michael Deacon |newspaper=《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》 |date=2010-10-15 |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/bbc/8067325/Mark-Gatiss-the-journey-of-a-geek-made-good.html |location=伦敦 |accessdate=2012-02-08 |archive-date=2011-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110202121235/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/bbc/8067325/Mark-Gatiss-the-journey-of-a-geek-made-good.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==早期写作==

由于他童年对《神秘博士》的喜爱，加蒂斯的早期作品都与该节目相关。他最早出版的幻想小说是一系列通过Virgin Publishing的《神秘博士》 [[:en:Virgin_New_Adventures|新冒险]]系列故事，第一部是1992年的''[[:en:Nightshade_(Doctor_Who)|Nightshade]]''。这些作品中，加蒂斯试图修正导致此节目在1989年取消的问题。<ref name=sundayherald /> 

他写的第一部剧本是一个[[:en:BBV|BBV]]录像带节目，称为''[[:en:P.R.O.B.E.|P.R.O.B.E.]]''：四部低成本，短片 《神秘博士》衍生电影。尽管这些电影中有前任博士[[乔恩·珀特维|乔恩·珀特维]]、[[科林·貝克|科林·貝克]]和[[彼得·戴維森|彼得·戴維森]]，但没有释出DVD版本。在2004年的一次采访中，他说不会授权重新释出，把它们看作一次练习。<ref name=sundayherald />

他最早有对许可的《神秘博士》作出的贡献包括四部[[:en:Doctor_Who_spin-offs#Original_fiction|小说]]，四部广播剧（两部是为BBV，另两部是为[[:en:Big_Finish_Productions|Big Finish Productions]]）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bigfinish.com/28-Doctor-Who-Invaders-from-Mars |title=''Doctor Who - Invaders From Mars'' |accessdate=2012-02-08 |archive-date=2008-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080913221741/https://www.bigfinish.com/28-Doctor-Who-Invaders-from-Mars |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bigfinish.com/02-Doctor-Who-Phantasmagoria |title=''Doctor Who - Phantasmagoria'' |accessdate=2012-02-08 |archive-date=2012-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120310072518/http://www.bigfinish.com/02-Doctor-Who-Phantasmagoria |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==表演==
===《绅士联盟》===
加蒂斯可能最知名于短片喜剧系列《[[绅士联盟|绅士联盟]]》团队（与演员[[:en:Reece_Shearsmith|Reece Shearsmith]]、[[:en:Steve_Pemberton|Steve Pemberton]]和联合编剧[[:en:Jeremy_Dyson|Jeremy Dyson]]一起)。他在上完大学之后花了一年环游欧洲之后，在不到20岁时上了一所戏剧学校，认识了他的联合编剧和演员。

《[[绅士联盟|绅士联盟]]》舞台剧开始表演于1995年，1997年在[[:en:Edinburgh_Festival_Fringe|Edinburgh Festival Fringe]]赢得了[[:en:Edinburgh_Comedy_Awards|Perrier Award]]。<ref name="telegraphgeek" />同年，此节目在[[:en:BBC_Radio_4|BBC Radio 4]]播出，名为''[[:en:On_the_Town_with_The_League_of_Gentlemen_(radio_series)|On the Town with the League of Gentlemen]]''，1999年开始在[[英國廣播公司第二台|英國廣播公司第二台]]电视上播出。这个电视节目让加蒂斯和他的同事赢得了[[英國學術電視獎|英國學術電視獎]]、[[:en:Royal_Television_Society|Royal Television Society]]奖和有名的[[:en:Golden_Rose_of_Montreux|Golden Rose of Montreux]]。

2005年，影片''[[:en:The_League_of_Gentlemen's_Apocalypse|The League of Gentlemen's Apocalypse]]''发布，但评价下降。这个喜剧团队没有解散，他们可能在未来重新共同工作。<ref name="telegraphgeek" />

===其他电视工作===
加蒂斯的电视工作包括为2001年复活''[[:en:Randall_&_Hopkirk_(Deceased)|Randall & Hopkirk]]''编剧和2003年为流行小品《[[小不列颠|小不列颠]]》编写脚本，并且在两个节目中都客串演出。2001年，他在''[[:en:Spaced|Spaced]]''中出演一个邪恶的公务员，这个角色模仿《[[駭客任務|駭客任務]]》系列电影的[[:en:Agent_Smith|Agent Smith]]。同年，他在纪录片[http://uk.imdb.com/title/tt0280310/ "SF:UK"] {{Wayback|url=http://uk.imdb.com/title/tt0280310/ |date=20120320051220 }}的一些集里。其他演出包括，喜剧戏剧''[[:en:In_the_Red_(novel)|In the Red]]''（[[英國廣播公司第二台|英國廣播公司第二台]]，1998）、惊悚喜剧''[[:en:Nighty_Night|Nighty Night]]''（[[英國廣播公司第三台|英國廣播公司第三台]]，2003）、[[:en:Agatha_Christie's_Marple|Agatha Christie's Marple]]的The Murder at the Vicarage中演出Ronald Hawes、2004年在[[:en:Vic_&_Bob|Vic & Bob]]系列''[[:en:Catterick_(TV_series)|Catterick]]''中客串出演和在''[[:en:The_Quatermass_Experiment|The Quatermass Experiment]]''经典科幻系列的[[:en:The_Quatermass_Experiment_(2005)|2005年重拍]]。<!-- A second series of ''Nighty Night'' and the new comedy-drama ''[[:en:Funland|Funland]]'', the latter co-written by his ''League'' cohort [[:en:Jeremy_Dyson|Jeremy Dyson]], both featured Gatiss and aired on 英國廣播公司第三台 in the autumn of 2005. He appeared as [[:en:Johnnie_Cradock|Johnnie Cradock]], alongside ''Nighty Night'' star [[:en:Julia_Davis|Julia Davis]] as [[:en:Fanny_Cradock|Fanny Cradock]], in ''Fear of Fanny'' on 英國廣播公司第四台in October 2006, and featured as Ratty in a new production of ''[[:en:The_Wind_in_the_Willows_(2006_film)|The Wind in the Willows]]'' shown on 英國廣播公司第一台on 1 January 2007. He wrote and starred in the 英國廣播公司第四台docudrama ''[[:en:The_Worst_Journey_in_the_World_(docudrama)|The Worst Journey in the World]]'', based on the memoir by polar explorer [[:en:Apsley_Cherry-Garrard|Apsley Cherry-Garrard]].-->

