From December 2010 to March 2011 Gatiss was playing the role of Bernard in [[:en:Alan_Ayckbourn|Alan Ayckbourn]]'s ''Season's Greetings'' at the [[:en:Royal_National_Theatre|Royal National Theatre]] in London alongside [[:en:Catherine_Tate|Catherine Tate]].

